      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/vitamin-d-and-human-health-23-publications-in-a-special-issue-from-2013/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/attachments/d3.mock.pdf&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-file-pdf&#34; style=&#34;margin-right: 0.3em;&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Download the single ZIP file of all of the publications from VitaminDWiki&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;OR - click on links to individual papers&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Some of these papers are in VitaminDWiki&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Citations are as of Oct 2019 – approximately 6 years after publication&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;h5 id=&#34;vitamin-d-and-human-health-celebrating-diversity&#34;&gt;Vitamin D and Human Health: Celebrating Diversity&lt;/h5&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;by Simon Spedding&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Nutrients 2014, 6(1), 11-14; &lt;a href=&#34;https://doi.org/10.3390/nu6010011&#34;&gt;https://doi.org/10.3390/nu6010011&lt;/a&gt; - 19 Dec 2013   Cited by 4&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Abstract&lt;/strong&gt; This Special Issue of Nutrients: Vitamin D and Human Health celebrates diversity in vitamin D research with articles from bench-to-bedside, examining mechanisms, epidemiology, and clinical issues in the management of non-skeletal disease following themes set by an earlier review in Nutrients &lt;sup&gt;[1]&lt;/sup&gt;. &lt;span&gt;[&amp;hellip;]&lt;/span&gt; Read more.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
